## 13. Low-Stock Alerts

### How It Works

* Each product has a reorder threshold
* Default threshold = 5
* Alerts trigger automatically when stock is low

### Admin Actions

* View alerts
* Dismiss alerts
* Update thresholds

### Advanced Behavior

* MySQL trigger ensures alerts fire on any stock update

